verbose_text: Microarray analysis of miRNAs showed that the expression levels of miR159, miR169, miR172, miR838, miR854, miR5658, csa-miRn6-3p, csa-miRn7-5p and csa-miRn8-3p were significantly altered in the CGMMV infected cucumber leaves at 10, 30 and 50 dpi.
